          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Rescinding DHS' Waiver Authority for Border Wall Act</b></p> <p>This bill repeals the Department of Homeland Security's authority to waive all legal requirements in order to ensure the expeditious construction of barriers and related roads along the border in the southwestern United States. <br> </p>]]></text>
